humanMachineDialogue.text: The report states that multiple (8) left axillary sentinel lymph nodes were excised and were negative for metastatic carcinoma (AJCC pN0 (i-)). This information aligns with New Rule 10 and New Rule 11, which indicate that N0 can indicate no metastatic carcinoma in sentinel lymph nodes and regional lymph nodes or that all assessed lymph nodes are negative for metastatic carcinoma. Therefore, the N stage for this patient's cancer is N0.
